Interface BagInterface<T>

public interface BagInterface<T>
An interface that describes the operations of a bag of objects.
Version:
5.0
Author:
Mohraiel Matta, Tiffany Truong, Erika Ledesma
Frank M. Carrano, Timothy M. Henry
